      <guid>http://urbanar-project-report.arjonagelhout.nl/</guid>
      <description>UrbanAR  An Augmented Reality Design Tool for Urban Design and Planning 
   About UrbanAR We want to make the urban design and planning process of our cities more fun and engaging: to make our cities more of a collaborative effort and better for everyone. Currently, municipalities are using old methods to get input from citizens, but we can change that!
That’s why we set out to create UrbanAR.</description>
